sentences.english: Convenient cable organizer keeps cables tangle-free.

sentences.english: Entanglement, meanwhile, is the roping together of particles in order to add more qubits.
sentences.chinese: 而缠结则是编结粒子，以此增加丘比特数。

sentences.english: She teased out the knots in her hair.

sentences.chinese: CAA往往同时伴有老年斑和神经原纤维缠结。

sentences.english: A tangled kelp forest fills the water column off the coast of Maine.
sentences.chinese: 缠结的海带森林弥漫着水柱沿海海面的缅因州。

sentences.english: Dislocation pile-up and tangling around carbide particles were also observed after high degree of deformation.
